trans-unit.source:
\n

Specifies the data type of a field, a property, or a Parameter object of a .NET Framework data provider.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxxx xxx xxxx xxxx xx x xxxxx$ x xxxxxxxx$ xx x $xxxxxx$Xxxxxxxxx$$xxxxxx$ xxxxxx xx x .XXX Xxxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A variable-length stream of non-Unicode characters ranging between 1 and 8,000 characters.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxxxx$xxxxxx xxxxxx xx xxx$Xxxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxx 0 xxx 0$000 xxxxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A fixed-length stream of non-Unicode characters.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxx$xxxxxx xxxxxx xx xxx$Xxxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A variable-length stream of binary data ranging between 1 and 8,000 bytes.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxxxx$xxxxxx xxxxxx xx xxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxx 0 xxx 0$000 xxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A simple type representing Boolean values of true or false.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx Xxxxxxx xxxxxx xx $xxxxxx$xxxx$$xxxxxx$ xx $xxxxxx$xxxxx$$xxxxxx$.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An 8-bit unsigned integer ranging in value from 0 to 255.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx 0$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxx xx xxxxx xxxx 0 xx 000.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A currency value ranging from -2 63 (or -922,337,203,685,477.5808) to 2 63 -1 (or +922,337,203,685,477.5807) with an accuracy to a ten-thousandth of a currency unit.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxxxx xxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx $0 00 $xx $000$000$000$000$000.0000$ xx 0 00 $0 $xx $000$000$000$000$000.0000$ xxxx xx xxxxxxxx xx x xxx$xxxxxxxxxx xx x xxxxxxxx xxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A type representing a date value.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx x xxxx xxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A type representing a date and time value.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx x xxxx xxx xxxx xxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Date and time data.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxx xxx xxxx xxxx.

trans-unit.source: Date value range is from January 1,1 AD through December 31, 9999 AD.
trans-unit.target: Xxxx xxxxx xxxxx xx xxxx Xxxxxxx 0$0 XX xxxxxxx Xxxxxxxx 00$ 0000 XX.

trans-unit.source:
Time value range is 00:00:00 through 23:59:59.9999999 with an accuracy of 100 nanoseconds.

\n
trans-unit.target: Xxxx xxxxx xxxxx xx 00$00$00 xxxxxxx 00$00$00.0000000 xxxx xx xxxxxxxx xx 000 xxxxxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Date and time data with time zone awareness.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxx xxx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source: Date value range is from January 1,1 AD through December 31, 9999 AD.
trans-unit.target: Xxxx xxxxx xxxxx xx xxxx Xxxxxxx 0$0 XX xxxxxxx Xxxxxxxx 00$ 0000 XX.

trans-unit.source: Time value range is 00:00:00 through 23:59:59.9999999 with an accuracy of 100 nanoseconds.
trans-unit.target: Xxxx xxxxx xxxxx xx 00$00$00 xxxxxxx 00$00$00.0000000 xxxx xx xxxxxxxx xx 000 xxxxxxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source: Time zone value range is -14:00 through +14:00.
trans-unit.target: Xxxx xxxx xxxxx xxxxx xx $00$00 xxxxxxx $00$00.

trans-unit.source:
\n

A simple type representing values ranging from 1.0 x 10 -28 to approximately 7.9 x 10 28 with 28-29 significant digits.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx 0.0 x 00 $00 xx xxxxxxxxxxxxx 0.0 x 00 00 xxxx 00$00 xxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A floating point type representing values ranging from approximately 5.0 x 10 -324 to 1.7 x 10 308 with a precision of 15-16 digits.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxxxx xxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxxx 0.0 x 00 $000 xx 0.0 x 00 000 xxxx x xxxxxxxxx xx 00$00 xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A globally unique identifier (or GUID).

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx $xx XXXX$.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An integral type representing signed 16-bit integers with values between -32768 and 32767.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx 00$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx $00000 xxx 00000.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An integral type representing signed 32-bit integers with values between -2147483648 and 2147483647.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx 00$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx $0000000000 xxx 0000000000.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An integral type representing signed 64-bit integers with values between -9223372036854775808 and 9223372036854775807.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx 00$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx $0000000000000000000 xxx 0000000000000000000.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A general type representing any reference or value type not explicitly represented by another DbType value.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxxxx xx xxxxx xxxx xxx xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxx $xxxxxx$XxXxxx$$xxxxxx$ xxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An integral type representing signed 8-bit integers with values between -128 and 127.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx 0$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx $000 xxx 000.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A floating point type representing values ranging from approximately 1.5 x 10 -45 to 3.4 x 10 38 with a precision of 7 digits.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxxxx xxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxxx 0.0 x 00 $00 xx 0.0 x 00 00 xxxx x xxxxxxxxx xx 0 xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A type representing Unicode character strings.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx Xxxxxxx xxxxxxxxx xxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A fixed-length string of Unicode characters.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxx$xxxxxx xxxxxx xx Xxxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An integral type representing unsigned 16-bit integers with values between 0 and 65535.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx 00$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx 0 xxx 00000.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An integral type representing unsigned 32-bit integers with values between 0 and 4294967295.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx 00$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx 0 xxx 0000000000.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An integral type representing unsigned 64-bit integers with values between 0 and 18446744073709551615.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx 00$xxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxx xxxxxxx 0 xxx 00000000000000000000.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A variable-length numeric value.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxxxx$xxxxxx xxxxxxx xxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A parsed representation of an XML document or fragment.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxxx xxxxxxxxxxxxxx xx xx XXX xxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxx.$$x$$x
